			<p class="meta"><span class="author">Posted by <a href="">staff</a>&nbsp;October 1st, 2012</span></p>
			<div class="entry">
			<p>The June 2012 of the UC Irvine Law Review, entitled &#8220;Governing the Magic Circle: Regulation of Virtual Worlds&#8220;, features articles of several prominent professors regarding issues of governance in online games and virtual worlds. All articles are available online.</p>
			</div>
