				<div class="post">
			<h2 class="title" id="post-784"><a href="http://cgvw.ics.uci.edu/ethnography-and-virtual-worlds/" rel="bookmark" title="Permanent Link to Ethnography and Virtual Worlds">Ethnography and Virtual Worlds</a></h2>
			<p class="meta"><span class="author">Posted by <a href="">staff</a>&nbsp;September 17th, 2012</span></p>
			<div class="entry">
			<p>Tom Boellstorff, Bonnie Nardi and two other colleagues have published the book &#8220;Ethnography and Virtual Worlds: A Handbook of Method&#8220;. A great read for students, teachers, designers, and scholars interested in using ethnographic methods to study online virtual worlds.</p>
			</div>
